# VacSim

VacSim is a Battery-Level-Aware Task Offloading Simulator designed for Intelligent Vacuum cleaners operating in Edge-Cloud Collaboration environments. It provides a framework for modeling battery consumption, task generation, and offloading policies to optimize battery life and task performance.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Create and activate a virtual environment
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # On Windows: .venv\Scripts\activate

# Install the package in development mode
pip install -e .

# Run a minimal example
vacsim run --config configs/experiments/basic_sim.yaml
```

